nodes.bodyText:
Well, you usually want to set defined or undefined mode, so consider this split:
doSetDefinedSize(CallbackDataProvider.CountCallback<T, ?> sizeCallback) {
            definedSize = true;
            sizeEstimateCallback = null;
            initialSizeEstimate = -1;
            this.sizeCallback = sizeCallback;
}

doSetUndefinedSize(SizeEstimateCallback<T, ?> sizeEstimateCallback, int initialSizeEstimate) {
           sizeCallback = null;
           definedSize = false;
           this.sizeEstimateCallback = sizeEstimateCallback;
           this.initialSizeEstimate = initialSizeEstimate;
}

And if you need to just set up the boolean definedSize you can do it with setter or directly.

